Good morning #love 🐞s. This is my #Mood as I draw closer to God. Acknowledging my shortcomings and humbly accepting my Greatness. The truth is I've gone through a lot over the past year (and maybe many of you have also). Emotionally, spiritually, verbally, financially, etc. Still I rise. I'm grateful for all of you who continually #support me. If you've downloaded my music, #ThankYou 
I say all this to say... Be encouraged. There's so much #beauty inside of you. Tap into it. #Embrace the quiet. #Understand your #balance. And stay #focused. You alone are #responsible for the #energy in your space. But Above all LOVE YOURSELF w your WHOLE 💖. Trust me, you're worth it. When it's all said and done your HEALTH and WELL BEING is your responsibility. #BeYou #BeLieve #LiveYourTruth #PreciateIt

from ignorant to vegan ... #achingheart#whatthefuck#wearemonsters#helptheplanet#helptheanimals#forourhealth#fortheenvironment#therainforest#thepoor#inlovewithlife#ourchildren#responsible#eatplants#compassionateliving#inpain#newchoices# van onwetendheid naar een veganistische levensstijl... Het begon allemaal toen ik een half jaar geleden per ongeluk een filmpje zag van de dagelijkse gang van zaken in een Frans slachthuis. Ik was in shock!! Ben daarna in het onderwerp gedoken en viel van het een in het ander ... ik kan het geen plek geven, behalve dan rondlopen met een gevoel vol afgrijzen ; wat hebben we met onze wereld gedaan!! Hoe is het mogelijk!! Ons dagelijks eetpatroon ondersteund niet alleen het onnoembare dierenleed wat we veroorzaken, maar gaat nog veel verder dan dat; de veeindustrie houd de wereldhonger instant, veroorzaakt regenwoud kap, is een van de grootste milieu verontreinigers en is slecht voor onze eigen gezondheid..hoeveel redenen heb je nog nodig?  #gebrokenhart#monsterlijk#watetenwevandaag#bomenkap#regenwoud#derdewereld#honger#mindervlees#gezondeten#gezondleven#metelkaar#dierenliefde#natuur#verslaving

I need yarn. Badly. All i have is my stuff thats probably 7 years old by now. Its great for looming fluffy hats for the winter but i need not so floofy yarn to learn knew techniques. Im essentially a complete beginner. I know how to cast on, stitch a straight row, but thats it. I cant even take them off the needles lol! But i want to learn and it helps with home therapy on my hands. I think it even helps my anxiety. Hopefully i can save up some money and go to joanns. Have to wait and see what happens. Maybe ill treat myself next month for my bday. Lol yeah right ill be responsible and buy something for the house. Damn. .

Locally made products assure consumers that the products they are buying were made locally, contributing to jobs and opportunities locally.
As companies learn more about the carbon footprint of their sourcing strategy, finding resources that are closer to headquarters and the stores where they sell their products helps them reduce environmental impact of overseas shipping.

Shadow the dog aggressive German Shepherd has seen a few trainers already.. I took him and his owner to the dog park and his owner thought this would never be possible with his dog. He was blown away.  A responsible owner looking for help should never be ripped off but helped. Taking advantage of people that are trying there best is Bad Karma. His last trainer calls himself the best dog trainer. What a joke. I have been fortunate enough to have a mentor  thats probably one of the best in the world but don't claim to be the best and don't rip people off.. #shepherd #k9 #ripoff #fake #goodhomes #start #with #responsible #owners #obedience #training #boxer #mastiff #pitbulls #bulldog #terrier #bulletproofpitbulls #tough #family #help #people #take #advantage #of the #weak
